      },
      "lineNbr": 250,
      "author": {
        "id": 5015
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-10-31T14:44:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m voting A for now.  My reasoning is that the jobs which did get canceled will show up as such in the search results, so it should be easy to just hit the button again to retry, or refresh the page to update the results list and then try again.  I think the most common reason for cancel to fail is that the job is finished (or canceled by someone else) between the page load and the cancel request.",
      "parentUuid": "aa694944_0ade7321",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 250,
        "startChar": 10,
