      "writtenOn": "2017-10-30T20:58:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Can you explain? Here\u0027s my understanding:\n\u003e var job;\nundefined\n\u003e !job\ntrue\n\u003e job \u003d {};\n{}\n\u003e !job\nfalse\n\u003e job.status \u003d\u003d undefined;\ntrue\n\u003e job.status \u003d \"\";\n\"\"\n\u003e !job || job.status \u003d\u003d undefined || job.status \u003d\u003d null\nfalse",
      "parentUuid": "cdcfae8e_0db97d71",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 272,
        "startChar": 17,
