      "writtenOn": "2017-10-31T14:54:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "sgtm.  (!job || !job.status \u003d\u003d null) does the same thing as (!job || job.status \u003d\u003d undefined || job.status \u003d\u003d null) if you want to be more concise (and please add a comment that double equals is intentional.  \n\nOtherwise, some future person may be tempted to replace it with !job.status if they don\u0027t know or remember \"\" is valid.",
